{"tid":1576541,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重失眠撚","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T14:27:53.000Z","uid":198798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1b014578d2ef489965246c3c03d05454443b7b","tid":1576541,"uid":198798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"以前一直都有失眠既習慣但係通常之黎會訓得返<br />\n近依個禮拜 連續2晚都無訓過 睇完醫生話我有d焦慮 開左d血清素同助眠藥（苦到仆街）先有覺好訓 但係長遠黎講唔想太依賴藥物<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依幾日完全訓唔到既原因係一放鬆訓個人就好似沉左落去咁 好唔舒服 一係就黎訓個下好似唔記得呼吸咁（本身有心悸） 好驚 一驚就訓唔到<br />\n有無同病相憐既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5d0f90c5eb6c3e9ed4409ab4c22b49852751ac","tid":1576541,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"fa699f9ec30cc0e4b43188a3e8d42ef5b89c07f2","tid":1576541,"uid":302752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"係咪壓力太大 試下做運動啦"},{"pid":"80771b4e2467c82c2d1b52b634b61968b282a9ec","tid":1576541,"uid":198798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa699f9ec30cc0e4b43188a3e8d42ef5b89c07f2","tid":1576541,"uid":302752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"係咪壓力太大 試下做運動啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"少做運動 無壓力 係個人無所事事 故思亂想屈出病來<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60